Simple library to validate usernames and passwords against an LDAP server.

Example:

ldap.yml example

development:
  host: 1.2.3.4
  base: dc=domain,dc=edu
  username: my_user
  password: my_password
  attrs: mail givenname sn
  result_set_limit: 100
  
===========================

usage:

class User
	include Dapper
	
	has_ldap_connection "<path to ldap.yml>"
end
